e49e6c59a3190ecc9eef0","tid":2459621,"uid":383871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T08:37:33.000Z","msg":"返工攰到死狗咁都陪我傾電話聽我講無聊嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T08:57:49.000Z","msg":"講任何無聊嘢對方都會笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b62b942ce531e0eaa5253c534ef4182c23bb1540","tid":2459621,"uid":41009,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T13:07:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda9ee9731418bef8f3b55de98c7281de273ef5c","tid":2459621,"uid":197813,"like":45,"dislike":2,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T16:14:35.000Z","msg":"驚我m痛所以買咗m痛藥擺係佢屋企話隨時可以俾我食<br />\n<br />\n買咗部電腦俾我做生日禮物 又整咗生日蛋糕俾我食 最重要係佢用部電腦整咗個ppt同我深情告白 佢本身無讀大專 中五畢業就無再讀 所以無乜點用過ppt 雖然個ppt淨係打咗啲字同up咗幾張相但佢都話整咗兩個鐘 搞到我一邊睇一邊感動到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有我鍾意嘅運動佢都肯陪我玩 明明佢都唔識應該會驚悶 但都陪我玩 我問佢同唔同埋我啲fd一齊玩佢又話驚自己太渣 唔敢同我地一齊玩 話會俾心機學 等佢再勁啲先同埋我啲fd一齊玩 我覺得佢肯學我嘅興趣好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有有次我病咗 佢男人老狗竟然煲粥俾我食 佢本身唔識整嘢食 但嗰陣我勁無胃口 夾硬食咗兩啖就無食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我愛你呀男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac92f086ab2f02dbe5705c9321887fcd39856c87","tid":2459621,"uid":242110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:10:57.000Z","msg":"無"},{"pid":"e4d287b522bd19bbc45b355d28813360bfa90464","tid":2459621,"uid":239492,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:17:34.000Z","ms